{"_path":"/city/t041","_dir":"city","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","title":"低收及中低收入戶醫療補助服務","description":null,"image":"/images/city/t041-1.jpeg","sequence":38,"category":"低收入補助","author":"市政府 社會局","link":"https://www.facebook.com/share/p/z4Y87u8LdT7Fnhbg/","head":{"meta":[{"name":"keywords","content":""},{"name":"robots","content":""},{"name":"author","content":""},{"name":"copyright","content":"© 2024 A7新林口-社區網站"},{"name":"og:title","content":"地方行政"}]},"publishedAt":"2024-11-15T00:00:00.000Z","toc":true,"body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"低收及中低收入戶醫療補助服務"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"低收及中低收入戶醫療補助服務 🚑"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"身體健康是許多人的日常所求，但只要是人難免都會有不小心生病受傷的時候 😰 如果因為經濟問題而耽誤病情反而得不償失！我們都能理解民眾的困難，桃園市政府 👉🏻 針對指定對象，提供最高 30 萬的醫療補助款 💰 期盼透過補助，讓市民不要因擔心荷包而延誤就醫！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"桃園市市民醫療補助對象須設籍於桃園市 👍🏻"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n補助對象分為兩種："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n1️⃣ 列為桃園市之低收入戶"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n2️⃣ 患有嚴重傷病，且最近 3 個月內自行負擔醫療費用超過 3 萬元，並符合下列情形之一："},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 列冊之中低收入戶"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 領有身心障礙者生活補助費"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 領有中低收入老人生活津貼"},{"type":"element","tag":"br","props":{},"children":[]},{"type":"text","value":"\n🔺 家庭總收入平均分配全家人口，每人每月不超過本市當年度最低生活費標準之 1.5 倍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"只要符合以上條件，提出申請，就有機會獲得醫療補助款最高 30 萬 💰 減輕家庭的經濟負擔！\n想了解更多詳細補助資訊，請至"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sab.tycg.gov.tw/News_Content.aspx?n=7355&s=684774"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":